title: #92Noon! PA & Charch
description: The Twins incredible 8 homer game against the Angels. Kevin Gorg and Brian Arrigoni in studio to talk some MIAC. Finally we feast. North Star legend, Mike Madano, calls in to talk his new position as Executive Adviser for the Wild.  Erin Cole from MN Historical Society calls to help us celebrate the lasting impact of Prince and the Minnesota music scene as First Avenue turns 50 next year. And Marnie Gellnar joins the last segment.
